{"type": "article", "id": 37115, "title": "酒店集团也要做生活方式，以及，sacai 2017 秋冬系列不错 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2017-01-23T03:32:36Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 3592, "name": "The North Face"}, {"id": 3865, "name": "adidas Originals"}, {"id": 9519, "name": "Thom Browne"}, {"id": 10726, "name": "Dior Homme"}, {"id": 12231, "name": "Sacai"}, {"id": 36914, "name": "2017 秋冬男装"}, {"id": 36987, "name": "爱马仕丝巾"}, {"id": 36988, "name": "Raf Simmons"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 26, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170123110841VbZ3vE2t4mYLBX1O.jpg", "contents": "<h3>一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://www.cpp-luxury.com/lvmh-is-set-to-take-a-stake-of-up-to-10-in-italian-eyewear-maker-marcolin/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>LVMH 买了部分意大利眼镜制造商 Marcolin 的股票</strong></a> | 奢侈品集团 LVMH 购买了非上市公司，意大利眼镜制造商 Marcolin 的股票，份额在 5% 至 10％之间。据有关消息人士对 Bloomberg 透露，此举是要加强 LVMH 对眼镜生产的控制。</p><p><a href=\"http://luxe.co/post/53056/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>雅高酒店集团将整合旗下精品酒店品牌，创建一个全新的生活方式部门</strong></a> | 新部门集合的精品酒店品牌将包括创新型青年旅社品牌 Jo＆Joe，雅高集团持股的德国精品酒店品牌 25hours Hotels，以及法国精品酒店品牌 MamaShelter。从 2 月 1 日起，将由 Cedric Gobilliard 领导这个新的部门。Cedric Gobilliard 于 2009 年加入雅高，主要负责集团 Mercure 以及 Novotel 品牌在法国各省的业务运营。&nbsp;</p><p><a href=\"http://www.marketwatch.com/story/moodys-cuts-sears-credit-ratings-further-into-junk-territory-on-weak-sales-2017-01-20\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>国际评级机构穆迪，下调了美国西尔斯百货的信用评级</strong></a> | 上个周五，穆迪将西尔斯控股的信用评级从原来的 Caa1 下调至 Caa2。此前，西尔斯公告节日季同店销售额同比下降 12%-13%，公司业绩持续恶化。</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p><a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2017/1/hermes-brides-de-gala-love-90silk-scarf\" rel=\"nofollow\">爱马仕推出 2017 春季特别版「Brides de gala LOVE 90」丝巾</a>。这条方型丝巾有 Hermès 经典金镂皮革马蹬印花，特别加入了 280 个心作为点缀，为呼应主题，还首次使用了十边心形礼盒。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170123102336sgdKRHEU4BZvDCf8.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170123102348vUztQ3I2VZLROlPH.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170123102349oyPSd8vrRzWI1QBL.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170123102359EYNJr01ovebWdwMa.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>Raf Simons 与 adidas Originals 的 2017 春夏联名系列，由一双简约的黑白二色 Adilette 拖鞋开启。这双拖鞋的米白色皮革鞋面上缀有「Hold Firmly」与「This Side Up」的字样，黑色鞋底外侧还能看到 Raf Simons 与 adidas Originals 双方的 logo，定价为 120 欧元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170123102441Rn72VNDfWjF5pXg1.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201701231024513z4yhRVdl02YjnoQ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665450\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>Dior Homme 2017 秋冬男装系列发布，主打 Hardior （硬核 Dior）。如主题所示，该系列将高端剪裁与夜店文化结合，并加入了湖绿、深红与橘黄等醒目的色调，艺术化拼贴、像素图案以及金属配件细节。最后以拥挤的夜店画面作印花，遍布棒球夹克、披风和大衣出场。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170123102513vU0B3kj2hmobszey.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.504000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170123102513cD086VnOJL9A1lhG.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2017012310251367WvF2K3zRTjiayc.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170123102513h6uTaDOpzX3qMrex.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170123102514dB0sNwXm5cyhIPLC.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170123102514JedNyPLjO7hfbXtC.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170123102514VKkTY4eORAU8Wwbg.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170123102514rP96IpkUhJBlTz3K.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201701231025145bH8luJXpkEcv7YU.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170123102544NPgS0fi7sCO2avAz.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170123102544xhoY8EgDTClz2iVm.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170123102544Q3GOKXJ0qMULrEtm.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201701231025458dPAzMiLKC0Y2GDp.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170123102545O32hvU8HtZFdgqN6.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170123102545CETdhcM1IbUyK6z3.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170123102553uyoLtDYxhnA0Qw1m.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170123102553zQ1h7GrByRm0wLHI.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2017/1/sacai-2017-fall-winter-collection\" rel=\"nofollow\">sacai 的 2017 秋冬系列</a>，以「Cut Up」为主题。设计师阿部千登势将经典服饰进行拆解、重新创造出崭新的面貌。另外，与 The North Face Urban Exploration 的联名系列，成为了这一季 sacai 的最大亮点。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170123102608pFqYdya5oLOjcQ8f.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170123102608C4wNWAhmOJ6vkblI.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170123102608YC4VhI8RQ1lijm3q.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170123102608Y9ZgmaIqHbGyVT2F.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170123102608FvhOauJ5nVrRI4oN.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170123102608IJfbpcgl0wCR4QEY.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170123102609z4HhTEVdotSBNpjy.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170123102609RLXli08JDSoq3H9N.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170123102608JRBAfDWew7atn2TC.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170123102609jwMaI05ULSmRVoKq.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170123102609ghAxaqbGrifOlIKE.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201701231026092AvNJYGyFuRMEVcU.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170123102619Eh0z7NcuAH6a9ylC.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170123102619myZVv436WYzxP5Bc.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201701231026197hEi9tIj3XDuf0RG.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170123102619O2GacCMD7ZmgThIU.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170123102619uEignmNvhODRdpKP.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170123102620rx8k0LtgWBseGomh.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201701231026204UuqP1KlFopgCef3.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170123102622blfIEjJQ8T7nDeLU.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170123102622SBiHz4LEyG62Nxko.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170123102633IXrmZJyQo4vNgdqe.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170123102633Ajn94UWiKQoVfElG.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170123102633AsrZHyLzICS84YXi.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170123102634Bf7Rp2I4UQFb6Hji.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170123102634oVLQtudx4bw7IYJ2.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170123102634R4mgHE7pwvIubDZG.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170123102650FqIvrG2nWSOBHJit.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>在 Thom Browne 的 2017 秋冬男装系列中，设计师利用解构方式将男士服装分解再重组，夸张的纸样服套在模特儿身上，并以灰色调贯穿其中。独特的帽子和衣服材质，以及模特阴郁的妆容也很抢眼。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170123110236jSEgz0hkCKlUd8xe.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170123110236PT6N8sdUvgJlxC9i.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170123110236fiYdJmc5qlaR86tU.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201701231102375R34cq29Lo6Dpsmy.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170123110237EYk5MFzqKXiNhflQ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170123110259JV6CmfHSevAKLZjU.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201701231103030YXpZ69DBPgHdSMQ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170123110303SHP92F58lDGrvquN.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201701231103046IF9pJcj8EQuL7yN.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>为纪念 Converse Chuck Taylor All Star 诞生 100 周年，特别推出了&nbsp;1950 年代的 All Star 的复刻款。这双鞋将会于日本制造，而鞋身帆布更特别用上了由创立于 1948 年日本的老字号布料品牌“富士金梅”出产的帆布，较浅的鞋头加上鞋边加粗了的红色水线凸显复古感。这双「ALL STAR J VTG 50 HI」鞋款将于 3 月上架，定价为 19440 日元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170123105147H9vVRBDZ6cWw3mlF.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170123105148kqNmMjiuU4dCg0OY.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170123105148oIm6rCJeuiKx79bG.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170123105154T06fk2Mjzibw7qHN.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>题图来自：<a href=\"http://wwd.com/runway/mens-fall-collections-2017/paris/thom-browne/review/\" rel=\"nofollow\">wwd</a></p>"}